						<p>Damaged. This records a gift of ninety sheep by Kiḻāvaṉ Dēvaṉkēsari <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kuñjiramallap Pallavaraiyan of Perumpaṉṟūr in Vēḷār-nāḍu (a sub-division) of Chōḷanāḍu to burn a perpetual lamp to the god of Tiruvoṟṟiyūr.</p>						

